title: Deacon Blue - Live At The Glasgow Barrowlands [2017,BDRip,720p]
description: Deacon Blue - Live At The Glasgow Barrowlands [2017,BDRip,720p] 'Live at the Glasgow Barrowlands' was filmed at Glasgow's iconic Barrowland Ballroom and on the last night of the band's UK 'Believers Tour'. Deacon Blue "Believers" and their best-loved songs from their 30-year career. This unforgettable performance is their first official live product in 10 years and the band's first ever live DVD & Blu-ray release.
